body:
**Nonexistent+ is a mod that adds a lot of swords, tools, materials, armor and some other interesting things to the game**. The latest versions of the mod add 6 basic materials (Distolium, Kronolium, Enderium, Netherium, Titanium, The Ultimarium) and 2 additional (Astral Stone and Retorium Crystal). 

**Nonexistent+ adds a possibility to create swords by combining standard and mod's materials.** As example, with this mod you can create an **Iron-Coated Diamond Sword** by adding **Iron Ingots** and **Iron Nuggets** to the **Diamond Sword** on the crafting table. **But what about materials that doesn't have nuggets?**
**Nonexistent+** adds **shards** for such materials! Each material will give you 4 shards for 1 item, except **Obsidian**, that gives 6. There are 10 different shards for now: Diamond, Emerald, Obsidian, Distolium, Kronolium, Enderium, Netherium, Titanium, The Ultimarium and Astral.

**Nonexistent+** also adds **9 new swords with special abilities** and **reinforced pickaxes** from various materials!
Many items are **animated**, and the mod have **over 40 advancements**!

